snippet.title: Legend of Rune Kickstarter Trailer
snippet.description:
Kickstarter Trailer for Legend of Rune, a new gay / yaoi visual novel with puzzle and RPG elements. 

You can find our Kickstarter page here:
https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/legendofrune/legend-of-rune-a-bl-yaoi-visual-novel-rpg

Credits:
Video Editing: SMoth
Music: Lionface
Sprite, CG, & BG Art: Fuyuure
Logo: Potouto
Puzzle UI: Atomic-Invasion
Voice of Rune: Melifiry
